{
  "analysis": "The last command output is showing the tail of is_in_shadow, but the earlier outputs (rodata, vector helpers, ray helpers, sphere_intersect, plane_intersect, sky_color) were likely truncated. I need to capture each piece separately in files and view small ranges to avoid truncation.",
